<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>회원가입 - community</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/style.css'>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>
      <a class="appbar" href="/">community</a>
    </h1>
  </header>
  <section>
    <h2>회원가입</h2>
    <form action="/auth/register_process" method="post">
      <p>커뮤니티에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</p><br>
      <p>사용할 이름을 입력하세요.</p>
      <p><input type="text" name="name" placeholder="이름"></p>
      <p>사용할 비밀번호를 입력하세요.</p>
      <p><input type="password" name="password" placeholder="비밀번호"></p>
      <p>사용할 비밀번호를 한번 더 입력하세요.</p>
      <p><input type="password" name="password2" placeholder="비밀번호"></p>
      <p><input type="submit" value='가입하기'></p>
    </form>
  </section>
  <footer>
    Community Service. Developed By kraftenty@gmail.com
  </footer>
</body>
</html>